  "prompt_type": "cognitive",
  "prompt_text": "Explain how DNS resolution works, step by step, from typing a URL to receiving a response.",
  "response_text": "Step 1: User Input (Q): The user types a URL (e.g., www.example.com) into a web browser.\n\nStep 2: URL Parsing (P): The browser separates the domain name (example.com) from the protocol (http or https).\n\nStep 3: Hostname Resolution (G): The browser checks the hostname's IP address in its local DNS cache. If it finds the IP address, it skips to step 7.\n\nStep 4: Recursive Query (A): If the IP address is not found in the local DNS cache, the browser sends a recursive query to a DNS resolver (usually provided by the Internet Service Provider).\n\nStep 5: Root Name Servers (C): The DNS resolver queries the Root Name Servers for the .com Top-Level Domain (TLD) name servers.\n\nStep 6: TLD Name Servers (C): The Root Name Servers respond with the IP addresses of the .com TLD name servers. The DNS resolver then queries these TLD name servers for the IP address of the example.com name server.\n\nStep 7: Authoritative Name Servers (C): The TLD name servers respond with the IP addresses of the authoritative name servers for example.com.\n\nStep 8: Authoritative Query (A): The DNS resolver queries the authoritative name servers for the IP address of www.example.com.\n\nStep 9: Response (A): The authoritative name servers respond with the IP address of www.example.com.\n\nStep 10: Cache Update (P): The DNS resolver updates its local DNS cache with the IP address of www.example.com.\n\nStep 11: Connection (A): The browser establishes a connection with the web server at the IP address received and requests the webpage.\n\nStep 12: Response (A): The web server sends the requested webpage to the browser.\n\nStep 13: Display (V): The browser displays the webpage to the user.\n\n---VCP RATINGS---\nA (Analytical Precision): 10\nV (Verbal Fluency): 9\nG (Goal Directedness): 10\nP (Pattern Recognition): 10\nE (Epistemic Confidence): 10\nQ (Query Interpretation): 10\nC (Contextual Awareness): 10\nY (Affective Modeling): 0 (As a text-based AI, I don't have emotions)